Key Match Events: Kalidou Koulibaly produced one of the first attempts at goal in the 18th minute.
Mane scored from a direct free-kick in the 96th minute to secure Senegal's 1-0 win.
Patrick Mwaungulu produced a rare shot at goal for Malawi early on.
Pape Gueye, Nicolas Jackson, and Boulaye Dia produced scoring chances in quick succession after the hour mark.
